== Overview ==

Final Fantasy IV features numerous enemies across different dungeons and areas. This page documents enemy statistics, abilities, and behaviors.

== Enemy Data Structure ==

Each enemy entry is 32 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00-$01 || 2 || HP
|-
| $02-$03 || 2 || MP
|-
| $04 || 1 || Level
|-
| $05 || 1 || Attack
|-
| $06 || 1 || Attack Multiplier
|-
| $07 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $08 || 1 || Defense Multiplier
|-
| $09 || 1 || Magic Defense
|-
| $0A || 1 || Magic Defense Multiplier
|-
| $0B || 1 || Agility
|-
| $0C-$0D || 2 || Experience
|-
| $0E-$0F || 2 || Gil
|-
| $10-$11 || 2 || Drop item ID
|-
| $12 || 1 || Drop rate
|-
| $13 || 1 || Elemental weakness
|-
| $14 || 1 || Elemental resistance
|-
| $15 || 1 || Status immunity
|-
| $16-$1F || 10 || AI script, attack patterns
|}

